snippet.title: Last Vanguard - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Last Vanguard is Out Now con Steam:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1729180/Last_Vanguard/

Explore a war-torn world ruled by an evil tyrant. Face a wide variety of enemies as you customize your strategy, switch weapons, and unlock diverse abilities.
